Text: Itinerary for Vegas trip Cc also attached the text file version of this better printing ITINERARY FOR James Lokay ZQQP Steve Hecht ZQXCO SOUTHWEST AIRLINES Outbound Trip Houston Hobby to Las Vegas Date Day Flight Routing Jun Thu Depart Houston Hobby HOU at PM and arrive in Phoenix PHX at PM Connect in Phoenix PHX at PM and arrive in Las Vegas LAS at PM Return Trip Las Vegas to Houston Hobby Date Day Flight Routing Jun Sun Depart Las Vegas LAS at AM and arrive in Houston Hobby HOU at AM The Venetian Hotel Las Vegas NV Las Vegas Blvd S Las Vegas NV Reservations under name of Danny Yee Pager Get Your Private Free Email from MSN Hotmail at Vegastxt

hi from vegasLittle Mell Vegas is nice It has visibly changed since we were last here Lots of new HotelCasinos The concert was very good We came in very late due to travel delays and missed the first of Lenny Kravitz and all of Cheryl Crow My Lagerfeld satchel didnt survive its gate check ordeal all the contents were fine though so I now have a reasonably nice new bag ala Southwest Airlines baggage office Ill give you details later Last night after the concert we grabbed a couple of hot dogs and wandered through some casinos While waiting for Steve to go to an ATM I killed some time by putting a into a nickel slot machine and won nickels Later while waiting for Steve to use the facilities I won on a quarter slots machine So far so good Give me a call The number here is Ask for Danny Yees room I love you Jim Get Your Private Free Email from MSN Hotmail at
